author: jsdelfino
msg: Axis2Client now sets the return value into the invoked Operation object without having to rely on the fact that the client knew the return type ahead of time. Generated CPP proxies get the correct return value out the Operation object and do not assume anymore that it is stored in the placeholder that they set into it before calling invoke()
